Obstacle avoidance bot using turtlebot3 in gazebo and visualised using rviz
obstacle_avoidance_P.py uses proportional controller for smooth movement

Usage:
1. $ roslaunch turtlebot3_gazebo turtlebot3_world.launch
2. $ roslaunch turtlebot3_gazebo turtlebot3_gazebo_rviz.launch
3. $ rosrun ros_practice obstacle_avoidance_P.py
